doc.after: In August 2008 the Indonesian version of CHIP Magazine distributed a complimentary DVD containing more than 80 000 articles without images with its 11th anniversary edition This edition also featured a three page Wikipedia article titled Wikipedia When one thousand brains are better than one The article provided an extensive history of Wikipedia including the Indonesian Wikipedia as well as a description of the Wikimedia Indonesia chapter which was in preparation at that time 22
